&lt;p&gt;&lt;sup&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;sub&gt;My curiosity was piqued by &lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/questions/43409756/r-efficiently-separate-groups-in-data-frame#comment73879642_43409986&quot;&gt;this exuberant comment&lt;/a&gt; &lt;em&gt;Brilliant! Orders of magnitude faster!&lt;/em&gt; to a &lt;code&gt;tidyverse&lt;/code&gt; answer of &lt;a href=&quot;https://stackoverflow.com/q/43409756/3817004&quot;&gt;a question&lt;/a&gt; which was closed as a duplicate of this question.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

